  "notes": "New Bark Town is the starting town of Pokemon Gold, Silver, and Crystal. It has no Pokemon Center or Poke Mart. The only healing available is the machine inside Elm's Lab (usable after receiving a starter). The east border is ocean water leading to Route 27 (Kanto), which requires Surf and is only accessible late-game. The town map tileset is TILESET_JOHTO. Silver (rival) appears outside Elm's Lab window early in the game (event flag EVENT_RIVAL_NEW_BARK_TOWN) and is scripted to shove the player away if spoken to before the lab theft. The teacher NPC runs a blocking script at coord events x=1,y=8 and x=1,y=9 to prevent the player from leaving west before obtaining a starter. Fish group is FISHGROUP_OCEAN for the eastern water tiles."
}
